research_stage.thaumicbases:tbusefire.1=§oCampfire§r - If a person wanders around for example in the forest when it is getting dark and he is too far away from home to go to his bed he is probably stuck there in the darkness with all those monsters around. You are a thaumaturge, sure you can solve that problem! You have discovered a way to make a campfire! To light it up you first need to right-click it with a log - magical logs may be more long-lasting. Next just insert any fuel in it. Now this little beacons!
